liard]] || ''The Washington Post''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1947|1948}} || Felix Belair Jr. || ''The New York Times''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1948|1949}} || Ernest B. (\"Tony\") Vaccaro || Associated Press\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1949|1950}} || Robert G. Nixon || International News Service\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1950|1953}} || Carlton Kent || ''[[Chicago Sun-Times]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1953|1954}} || Robert J. Donovan || ''New York Herald Tribune''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1954|1955}} || [[Anthony H. Leviero]] || ''The New York Times''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1955|1956}} || Laurence H. Burd || ''Chicago Tribune''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1956|1958}} || Francis M. Stephenson || ''[[Daily News (New York)|Daily News]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1958|1959}} || Marvin Arrowsmith || Associated Press\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1959|1961}} || Garnett D. Horner ||''The Washington Star''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1961|1962}} || William H.Y. Knighton Jr. || ''[[The Baltimore Sun]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1962|1963}} || Robert Roth || ''[[Philadelphia Bulletin]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1963|1964}} || Merriman Smith || United Press International\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1964|1966}} || Alan L. Otten || ''[[The Wall Street Journal]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1966|1967}} || Robert E. Thompson || [[Hearst Newspapers]]\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1967|1968}} || Frank Cormier || Associated Press\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1968|1969}} || Carroll Kilpatrick || ''The Washington Post''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1969|1970}} || Charles W. Bailey II || ''[[Minneapolis Tribune]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1970|1971}} || Peter Lisagor || ''[[Chicago Daily News]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1971|1972}} || John P. Sutherland || ''[[U.S. News & World Report]]''\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1972|1973}} || Edgar A. Poe || ''[[The Times-Picayune]]'' ([[New Orleans]])\n|-\n|}\n{{col-break}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Name\n! scope=\"col\" | Employer\n|-\n| {{Dash year|1973|1974}} || Ted Knap || [[Scripps-Howard Newspapers|Scripps Howard Newspapers]]\n|-\n| {{Dash yea